modName: Mercenary Armor RUSSIAN - Thieves guild Guildmaster armor unenchanted
summary:
Leather armor are made on the basis of the thieves\' guild armor
Armor can be crafted in the smithy (\"Leather\" section) and can be upgraded on the bench.
descriptionHtml:
Leather armor are made on the basis of the thieves\' guild armor.
Armor can be crafted in the smithy (\"Leather\" section) and can be upgraded on the bench.

[color=red][b] Please be warned this is not a new armor, just Thieves guild Guildmaster armor unenchanted!!![/b] [/color]

- Removed all enchantments

Install:

Copy esp file to your Skyrim DATA directory.


Kojanaya bronya Naemnika sdelanaya na osnove broni glavi gildii vorov.
Eto ne novaya bronia!
Bronya dostupna dlya krafta v kuznice i uluchsheniya na verstake.

- Ubrani vse zacharovaniya
